Experience held by the BRIDGE DESIGN ENGINEER: Criterion description: Experience in the position of Bridge Design Engineer and/or Structural Design Engineer and/or Works of Art Engineer in contract(s) where feasibility studies and/or technical projects for new construction and/or modernization and/or widening of highways, national roads, express roads, county roads, and urban streets that included bridges, passages, or viaducts with a minimum length of 200 meters each were prepared and/or updated and/or revised. Participation of the proposed expert in the position of Bridge Design Engineer and/or Structural Design Engineer and/or Works of Art Engineer in contract(s) where feasibility studies and/or technical projects for new construction and/or modernization and/or widening of highways, national roads, express roads, county roads, and urban streets that included bridges, passages, or viaducts with a minimum length of 200 meters each were prepared and/or updated and/or revised will be scored as follows:
- 2 bridges and/or passages and/or viaducts with a minimum length of 200 meters each: 3 points;
- 3 bridges and/or passages and/or viaducts with a minimum length of 200 meters each: 4.5 points;
- 4 or more bridges and/or passages and/or viaducts with a minimum length of 200 meters each: 6 points.

Additional information in section II.2.5) – Award criteria from the Instructions for Bidders.

