SSD storage capacity: Technical component.
a) If the bidder provides an SSD larger than 1TB, 20 points are awarded;
b) If the bidder provides an SSD of 1TB, 10 points are awarded;
c) If the bidder provides an SSD of 512 GB (the minimum requirement specified in this Specification), 0 points are awarded;
d) If the bidder provides an SSD smaller than 512 GB (the minimum requirement specified in this Specification), the offer will be declared non‑compliant.
No points are awarded for other intermediate values.

