peste 4 proiecte – 100,00 puncte, iar în urma aplicării ponderii de 15% rezultă un total de 15,00 puncte.

column4:
Project manager's experience in contract execution: The project manager's experience, expressed by the number of similar projects in which they have carried out the same type of activities as those to be performed in the future contract. Participation in completed projects (as of the deadline for submitting bids) in which the proposed expert has carried out activities similar to the position for which they are nominated. Scoring is awarded as follows:
