2 projects – 25.00 points, and after applying a weight of 15% the total is 3.75 points;
3–4 projects – 50.00 points, and after applying a weight of 15% the total is 7.50 points;
more than 4 projects – 100.00 points, and after applying a weight of 15% the total is 15.00 points.

column3:
