Environmental aspects: Number of electric and/or hybrid machines. Points will be awarded for the number of electric and/or hybrid machines that will actually be involved in the execution of the contract and that the bidding economic operator owns/has access to, as follows:
a) The bidder who proves that they own/have access to 1‑3 electric and/or hybrid machines that will be used in the contract execution (these are also listed in the Quantity Lists and Form C8 – LIST covering the hours of operation of construction machines submitted by the bidder) – 3 points;
