Perioada de garantie: Perioada de garantie acordata lucrarii, Pentru oferta care prevede cea mai mare perioada de garantie acordata lucrarii (exprimata in numar luni) in`cadrul procedurii de atribuire se acorda punctajul maxim alocat (10 puncte).
Pentru celelalte oferte, punctajul se acorda proportional, astfel:
Pn = (Gn - Gmin. acceptata)/(G max. - Gmin. acceptata) x 10
Unde:
o   Pn = punctajul ofertei ”n” pentru factorul de evaluare „Perioada de garantie acordata lucrarii”;
o   Gn = perioada de garantie ofertata de ofertantul pentru care se calculeaza punctajul;
o   Gmin. acceptata = perioada de garantie minim acceptata (36 de luni) in cadrul procedurii de atribuire;
o   G max. = perioada de garantie maxima acceptata (96 de luni) in cadrul procedurii de atribuire;
Note:
Perioada de garantie se va exprima in luni de la data intocmirii procesului verbal de receptie la terminarea lucrarilor;
Perioada maxima de garantie a lucrarii este de 96 de luni, iar perioada de garantie minima este de 36 de luni.
Sub durata de garantie a lucrarii minima de 36 de luni, oferta va fi declarata neconforma. Ofertele cu o durata de garantie mai mare de 96 luni nu vor fi punctate suplimentar.

column4:
Guarantee period: The guarantee period granted for the work. For the offer that provides the longest guarantee period for the work (expressed in number of months) within the award procedure, the maximum allocated score (10 points) is awarded.
For the other offers, the score is awarded proportionally as follows:
Pn = (Gn - Gmin.accepted) / (Gmax - Gmin.accepted) × 10
Where:
- Pn = the score of offer "n" for the evaluation factor “Guarantee period granted for the work”;
- Gn = the guarantee period offered by the bidder for which the score is calculated;
- Gmin.accepted = the minimum accepted guarantee period (36 months) within the award procedure;
- Gmax = the maximum accepted guarantee period (96 months) within the award procedure;
Notes:
- The guarantee period shall be expressed in months from the date of the acceptance protocol to the completion of the works;
- The maximum guarantee period for the work is 96 months, and the minimum guarantee period is 36 months.
- Offers with a guarantee period shorter than the minimum of 36 months will be declared non‑conforming. Offers with a guarantee period longer than 96 months will not receive additional points.

