column3:
Experienta profesionala a persoanei nominalizate ca Inginer proiectant instalatii pentru constructii sau echivalent pentru persoanele juridice straine: Experienta profesionala a persoanei nominalizate ca Inginer proiectant instalatii pentru constructii sau echivalent pentru persoanele juridice straine, Detalii privind aplicarea algoritmului de calcul
Se puncteaza experienta Inginer proiectant instalatii pentru constructii sau echivalent pentru persoanele juridice straine, concretizata in numarul de contracte in care persoana nominalizata a indeplinit acelasi tip de activitati ca cele pe care urmeaza sa le indeplineasca in viitorul contract:
a) pentru experienţa constând în implicarea persoanei propuse în 1 (un) contract de servicii de proiectare sau contract de lucrari care include si servicii de proiectare, se acordă 0 puncte, aceasta reprezentand cerinta minima solicitata;
b) pentru experienţa constând în implicarea persoanei propuse între 2 si 3 contracte de servicii de proiectare sau contracte de lucrari care includ si servicii de proiectare se acordă punctajul de 4 puncte;
c) pentru experienţa constând în implicarea persoanei propuse în 4 sau mai multe contracte de servicii de proiectare sau contracte de lucrari care includ si servicii de proiectare se acordă punctajul maxim de 8 puncte.

Se vor atasa documente-suport relevante care atestă experienţa specifică, cu titlu exemplificativ: fişa de post, contract de muncă, recomandare sau orice alte documente emise sau contrasemnate de beneficiar sau de executantul principal. Documentele suport prezentate trebuie sa indeplineasca urmatoarele conditii:
1.    Sa fie emis sau contrasemnat de beneficiar sau de prestatorul/contractantul principal sau de angajator;
2.    Din el sa reiasa numele persoanei nominalizate si specializarea pe care o detine;
3.    Din el sa reiasa tipurile de activitati indeplinite de persoana nominalizata, astfel incat sa se faca dovada ca aceasta a indeplinit in cadrul contractelor mentionate, acelasi tip de activitati ca cele pe care urmeaza sa le indeplineacsa in viitorul contract.

Prin sintagma «servicii de proiectare» se intelege: servicii de proiectare (la orice faza conform art. 5 din HG nr. 907/2017 sau echivalent pentru ofertantii straini,  pentru lucrari de instalatii pentru constructii
Prezenta sectiune se completeazacu prevederile din documentatia de atribuire, Sectiunea II, Caiet de sarcini, DETALII PRIVIND CRITERIUL DE ATRIBUIRE- Factori de evaluare.

column4:
Professional experience of the person nominated as Design Engineer for building installations or an equivalent for foreign legal entities: Professional experience of the person nominated as Design Engineer for building installations or an equivalent for foreign legal entities, Details regarding the application of the scoring algorithm
The experience of the Design Engineer for building installations or an equivalent for foreign legal entities is scored based on the number of contracts in which the nominated person has performed the same type of activities as those to be performed under the future contract:
a) For experience consisting of the proposed person’s involvement in 1 (one) design services contract or a work contract that also includes design services, 0 points are awarded, as this represents the minimum required;
b) For experience consisting of the proposed person’s involvement in between 2 and 3 design services contracts or work contracts that include design services, 4 points are awarded;
c) For experience consisting of the proposed person’s involvement in 4 or more design services contracts or work contracts that include design services, the maximum score of 8 points is awarded.

Relevant supporting documents attesting to the specific experience must be attached, for example: job description, employment contract, recommendation or any other documents issued or countersigned by the beneficiary or the main contractor. The supporting documents presented must meet the following conditions:
1. Be issued or countersigned by the beneficiary or the main service provider/contractor or the employer;
2. Clearly show the name of the nominated person and their specialization;
3. Clearly show the types of activities performed by the nominated person, so that it can be proven that they have carried out, within the mentioned contracts, the same type of activities as those to be performed under the future contract.

The term "design services" means: design services (at any phase in accordance with art. 5 of Government Decision no. 907/2017 or the equivalent for foreign bidders, for building installation works).
This section is to be completed with the provisions from the tender documentation, Section II, Specification Sheet, DETAILS REGARDING THE AWARD CRITERION – Evaluation Factors.

column3:
