Se puncteaza experienţa profesionala a Managerului de contract/Coordonatorului de contract - inginer specializat in domeniul construcții civile, industrial și agricole sau echivalent pentru persoanele juridice straine, concretizata in numărul de contracte similare în care persoana nominalizata a îndeplinit acelaşi tip de activităţi ca cele pe care urmează să le îndeplinească în viitorul contract.
a) pentru experienţa constând în implicarea persoanei propuse în 1 (un) contract se acordă 0 puncte, aceasta reprezentand cerinta minima solicitata;
b) pentru experienţa constând în implicarea între 2 şi 3 contracte a persoanei propuse se acordă punctajul de 7,5 puncte;
c) pentru experienţa constând în implicarea în 4 sau mai multe contracte a persoanei propuse se acordă punctajul maxim de 15 puncte;

Se vor atasa documente-suport relevante care atestă experienţa specifică, cu titlu exemplificativ: fişa de post, contract de muncă, recomandare sau orice alte documente emise sau contrasemnate de beneficiar sau de executantul principal sau de angajator. Documentele suport prezentate trebuie sa indeplineasca următoarele conditii:
1. Sa fie emis sau contrasemnat de beneficiar sau de executantul principal sau de angajator;
2. Din el sa reiasa numele persoanei nominalizate și specializarea pe care o detine;
3. Din el sa reiasa tipurile de activitati indeplinite de persoana nominalizata, astfel incat sa se faca dovada ca aceasta a detinut in cadrul contractelor similare mentionate, poziții/funcții similare prin prisma căreia a avut responsabilităţi și sarcini de Manager de contract/ Coordonator de contract.
Prin sintagma “contracte similare” autoritatea contractanta intelege: contracte de lucrări, conform art.3 alin.(1) lit. m) din Legea nr.98/2016, privind lucrări de constructii noi si/sau consolidări si/sau reabilitări (reparații capitale) si/sau modernizări si/sau extinderi la imobile de tip constructii civile si/sau industriale, cuprinse cel putin in categoria de importanta C conform prevederilor HG nr. 766/1997 actualizata
Prezenta sectiune se completeazacu prevederile din documentatia de atribuire, Sectiunii II, Caiet de sarcini, DETALII PRIVIND CRITERIUL DE ATRIBUIRE- Factori de evaluare.

column4:
Professional experience of the person nominated as Contract Manager/Contract Coordinator – a specialist engineer in the field of civil, industrial and agricultural construction or equivalent for foreign legal entities: Details regarding the application of the scoring algorithm.
The professional experience of the Contract Manager/Coordinator – specialist engineer in civil, industrial and agricultural construction or equivalent for foreign legal entities is scored based on the number of similar contracts in which the nominated person has performed the same type of activities as those to be performed in the future contract.
a) For experience consisting of involvement of the proposed person in 1 (one) contract, 0 points are awarded, as this represents the minimum requirement;
b) For experience consisting of involvement in 2 to 3 contracts, 7.5 points are awarded;
c) For experience consisting of involvement in 4 or more contracts, the maximum score of 15 points is awarded.

Relevant supporting documents must be attached to certify the specific experience, for example: job description, employment contract, recommendation or any other documents issued or countersigned by the beneficiary or the main contractor or the employer. The supporting documents presented must meet the following conditions:
1. Must be issued or countersigned by the beneficiary, the main contractor or the employer;
2. Must show the name of the nominated person and his/her specialization;
3. Must show the types of activities performed by the nominated person, so that it can be proven that within the mentioned similar contracts they held similar positions/functions that gave them responsibilities and tasks as a Contract Manager/Contract Coordinator.
By the term “similar contracts”, the contracting authority understands: work contracts, according to art.3 para.(1) lit. m) of Law no. 98/2016, regarding new construction works and/or consolidations and/or rehabilitations (major repairs) and/or modernisations and/or extensions of civil and/or industrial building properties, included at least in importance category C according to the provisions of Government Decision no. 766/1997 updated.
This section is to be completed in accordance with the provisions of the tender documentation, Section II, Specification, DETAILS REGARDING THE AWARD CRITERION – Evaluation Factors.

