column4:
Professional experience of the person nominated as Head of the design team – architect with signing authority – according to Law No. 184/2001 or equivalent legislation in the country where the bidder is resident: Details regarding the application of the scoring algorithm. The professional experience of the Head of the design team – architect with signing authority – is assessed based on the number of contracts in which the nominated person performed the same type of activities as will be required in the future contract.

